tellraw @p {"text":"How to Play:"}
tellraw @p {"text":"This is a PVP game where the last person/team/villager standing wins."}
tellraw @p {"text":"Players get five random items at the beginning of the game, and another item every 15.85 seconds."}
tellraw @p {"text":"Every player gets the same item. If you get a diamond sword, for example, know that everyone else has one too."}
tellraw @p {"text":"There are three modes: Free for all, where everyone is on their own team, teams, where there are two teams, and defense, where each team has to keep their villager alive (while the other destroys it)."}
tellraw @p {"text":"Good luck!"}